                            <comment id="12743518" author="jbellis" created="Sat, 15 Aug 2009 01:42:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d rather not call flush every add if possible.  What problems are you seeing?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(To be pedantic: the change in the revision in question moved from using an unbuffered writer, to using a buffered one.  Not removing a pre-existing flush.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744168" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 18:54:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch to always sync commitlog, either as a batch pre-ack (current CLSync of true) or a new periodic mode defaulting to ever 1000ms&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744172" author="lenn0x" created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 19:15:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thread.sleep(600) should be pulling in getCommitLogSyncPeriod()&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744173" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 19:16:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 w/ config option actually used &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744283" author="lenn0x" created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 23:31:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744285" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 23:37:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744765" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 18 Aug 2009 22:46:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;forgot while loop &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744767" author="lenn0x" created="Tue, 18 Aug 2009 22:47:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oops! Yes, this looks better now. +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12744768" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 18 Aug 2009 22:49:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12745065" author="hudson" created="Wed, 19 Aug 2009 14:08:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra #172 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/172/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/172/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
